text: The Wild Horse Stampede is a 1926 American silent western film directed by Clifford Smith and starring Jack Hoxie, Fay Wray and Marin Sais.Munden p.903 ==Cast== * Jack Hoxie as Jack Tanner * Fay Wray as Jessie Hayden * William Steele as Charlie Champion * Marin Sais as Grace Connor * Clark Comstock as Cross Hayden * Jack Pratt as Henchman * Art Mix as Henchman * Bert De Marc as Henchman * Monte Montague as Henchman ==References== ==Bibliography== * Munden, Kenneth White. The American Film Institute Catalog of Motion Pictures Produced in the United States, Part 1.
